sql:
SELECT COUNT(participant_id) AS treatment_count
FROM mental_health_history
WHERE current_treatment = 1;

external_knowledge:
- Large tech companies are defined as those with 50 or more employees; 
- Currently receiving mental health treatment refers to participants with a value of 1 in the current_treatment column;
- Severe negative consequences of mental and physical health issues are ranked using the RANK() function based on the values in the mental_health_consequence and phys_health_consequence columns.
